{
  "stem": "13833.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he took me into the police station, and I said, oh my god.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So all I could do is I put down the phone number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I called.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And comes-- what's his name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was the name of the ambassador.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Frightened.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I could see that he was so frightened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as he walks in, I started to hit him with the three words over and over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Mjolk, brod, [SWEDISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I see that his face relaxed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And of course, the Romanian didn't understand a word.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they let me go with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then we were almost at the car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He said, how did you come to this idea?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Did you forgetting I worked with Wallenberg?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that's what saved me, these three Swedish words.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So then, finally, they decided-- the Russians-- that we can leave with the 12 of them through Russia, and we can go to Sweden, the eight of us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was eight Swedes and these 12.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were ail happy we were out in [INAUDIBLE], you know, where they used to have the big bombing at the railway station.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And first the Swedes went on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the Russians suddenly said, nyet, and they wouldn't let  us go with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got stuck in Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was bad-- what I did that time, I could-- through the Red Cross, I could send letters to my parents.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- what did I do-- writing for a newspaper there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was eating frogs all the time because that-- I didn't have much money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they taught me how to take them out of the lake, and how to burn them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a very nice little room by a  lovely lady-- [CAR HORN] oh, please stop it-- lady.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
